title: Rachel Steele - Wunder Woman vs the Museum Curator
description:
This has been called a lot of things and the ID number from clips4sale has it listed as BestofWW26 which is misleading since there is already a different file of that name which is different. This is the clip where the museum curator (played by Kenny Cox) turns Diana Prince into a wax doll zombie. Then reveals her idendity as Wunder Woman. He has her way with her. and then saves her for his museum collection. 

File info : 720 x 480 HQ (not he high definition version) Not the original clip from clips for now. I did some audio editing for this clip since it was real bad and needed to be fixed
